{"tid":902871,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊聯機玩澳門格蘭披治!!!","createTime":"2018-11-15T06:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T14:30:30.000Z","uid":11222,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad299d88bfdf91510862fc06aab9c9c74f392d8","tid":902871,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"SEED: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B4MXYfqVm8K0Qkp4RHRDdzFPS0E&amp;usp=drive_web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffolderview%3Fid%3D0B4MXYfqVm8K0Qkp4RHRDdzFPS0E%26usp%3Ddrive_web&d=ZWcZKNvS28CkH%2Fe%2BhxUukHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ac718f6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=0B4MXYfqVm8K0Qkp4RHRDdzFPS0E&amp;usp=drive_web</a><br />\n<br />\nMACAU 賽道<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iESn8ylqx2w&amp;feature=related \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiESn8ylqx2w%26feature%3Drelated%20&d=ZWcZKNvS28CkH%2Fe%2BhxUukHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1b4ed3d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iESn8ylqx2w&amp;feature=related </a><br />\n<br />\n安裝後可玩可聯機(VLAN &gt;綜合區域(ETC)&gt;香港綜合區 ) 注:其他區是不能連線的 <br />\n因為VLAN 登入需要註冊成為會員的 <br />\nVLAN 註冊網址: <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ipve.com/bbs/register.php \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipve.com%2Fbbs%2Fregister.php%20&d=ZWcZKNvS28CkH%2Fe%2BhxUukHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=29cceb3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ipve.com/bbs/register.php </a><br />\n本遊戲為RACE 07+5 ADDITION (所以為12GB) <br />\n各位下載後為1.98GB FILE <br />\n解壓縮後為10.8 GB <span style=\"color: red;\">(解壓縮快慢與電腦硬件有關) </span><br />\nMinimum System Requirements <br />\n<br />\nSystem: <br />\nIntel Pentium IV 1.7 GHz or equivalent <br />\nRAM: <br />\n512 MB <br />\nHard Drive Space: <br />\n2500 MB <br />\n<br />\n安裝途中會彈出錯誤 , 但不用理會 <br />\n安裝後 , 亦有機會彈出圖下的錯誤 <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.douxie.com/upload/imgs/1106/1306907774112.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.douxie.com%2Fupload%2Fimgs%2F1106%2F1306907774112.jpg&h=79255c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請將Config.exe 同 Race_Steam.exe (右CLICK 內容 &gt; 相容性 &gt; TICK 左 以相容模式執行這個檔案 ( 選XP SP3 ) 按套用.... <br />\n<br />\n另外本身部機廢廢地既一定要入config.exe set 個setting <br />\n部機個Direct X同埋Display Card 一樣一定UPDATE 到最新 <br />\n<br />\n如何聯機? <br />\n登入VLAN 後進入遊戲 <br />\n選Multiplayer&gt;LAN (如果想開場按HOST) <br />\n如果在LAN 區域見到有SERVER , 但不能進入 <br />\n寫著: <br />\nYou can only join during practice or qualify sessions server version <br />\n意思是指SERVER 正進行比賽(要等HOST 轉返做PRACTICE 先可以進入) <br />\n<br />\n我都係照copy人地<br />\n有冇巴打一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167e9b7c70e5f45598973364af221fad337e7970","tid":902871,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb0c7e34950a3837903420c1a114839fcc6438ca","tid":902871,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"641cb216b31cb9e75afb3110fbe5b218edf78c66","tid":902871,"uid":20896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"路過幫你推下"},{"pid":"7087e780ceb763426aceb86fcdcde1d567f9aeda","tid":902871,"uid":1020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"高登加埋我諗都有搞左7年8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adcf0837b7a7ed2597a2ab9833dc5bed341ad54","tid":902871,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"以前有down過但冇同過巴打玩<br />\n係時間拎番個封緊塵既軚出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514b1dec8957a257020abc98dad46d3407077d53","tid":902871,"uid":11222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩試玩左一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咁撞"},{"pid":"7ec5